<div>Heath is a curious child who has vivid imagination. He enjoys helping out, playing outside, and showing affection. Heath has experienced a great deal of trauma in his life and can have challenging moments. He needs permanency and a family who is willing to offer him the support and unconditional love he deserves. He’s looking forward to having parents who can create consistent structure, advocate for his needs in school and build good social habits. With a loving family who can offer him structure and stability, he’ll be able to grow into his best self!</div>
